:TITLE:
Team Status Form
:CONTENT:
This form lists all Response Teams,
their assignment location, and the personnel composition.
Selecting a Response Team takes you to a Change: Response Team Form where you can 
:LIST:
Change the team's location assignment through the Address Selection Menu.
Remove personnel 
or Add personnel through the Personnel Selection Menu
Delete the team altogether.
:ENDLIST:
Selecting an address takes you to its Damage Assessment Form.
Selecting a person takes you to their Personnel Information Form.

Messages are sent to everyone concerned in the case of Personnel Changes.

